Razor is a launcher and assistant for the Ultima Online classic client.

== Getting Started ==

There is a [http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=j9aTGXPyFjY comprehensive video tutorial].

When Razor starts you will be shown the dialog below. If you have having trouble connecting, verify the server and port number for UOForever.
